org.safs.selenium.webdriver.lib

Class RS.XPATH.SAP

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.safs.selenium.webdriver.lib.RS.XPATH.SAP
  • Enclosing class:
    RS.XPATH

    public abstract static class RS.XPATH.SAP
extends java.lang.Object
    Defines arrays of search-conditions for SAPUI5 controls to be appended to RS.XPATH.DESCENDANTS_PREFIX or RS.XPATH.ALL_ELEMENTS_PREFIX to form a valid XPATH for searching.
    It serves as parameter of RS.XPATH.relativeDescendants(String[]) or RS.XPATH.allDescendants(String[])
